290
00:14:48,972 --> 00:14:50,263
<i>Daniel Atlas,</i>

291
00:14:51,641 --> 00:14:52,891
<i>Henley Reeves,</i>

292
00:14:54,894 --> 00:14:56,603
<i>Jack Wilder.</i>

293
00:14:57,397 --> 00:15:01,316
<i>Arthur Tressler and the MGM Grand</i>
proudly presents

294
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:06,154
<i>The Four Horsemen.</i>

295
00:15:06,489 --> 00:15:07,572
(AUDIENCE CHEERING)

296
00:15:07,657 --> 00:15:08,824
MERRITT: Thank you.

297
00:15:09,117 --> 00:15:11,326
Tonight we would like to try something

298
00:15:11,411 --> 00:15:13,829
that will, well, set us a bit apart.

299
00:15:13,997 --> 00:15:17,582
For our final trick,
we're gonna do something never before

300
00:15:17,667 --> 00:15:19,668
seen on a Las Vegas stage.

301
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:23,005
Or any stage for that matter.

302
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,298
Ladies and gentlemen,

303
00:15:27,593 --> 00:15:28,677
tonight

304
00:15:29,595 --> 00:15:31,346
we are going to rob a bank.

305
00:15:31,472 --> 00:15:33,181
(AUDIENCE CHEERING LOUDLY)

