00:16:08,593 --> 00:16:10,177
Oh, yeah, yeah, sure, of course.

312
00:16:10,261 --> 00:16:11,595
- (BEEPS)
- Let me just put this away.

313
00:16:11,846 --> 00:16:13,055
Actually, I need to take that.

314
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:15,015
After the show, I can come
and give it back to you.

315
00:16:16,392 --> 00:16:17,392
Okay.

